  &lt;p id="jIKsp4"&gt;Microsoft is launching its Xbox TV app on select Amazon Fire TV Sticks today. The app, which Microsoft first &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/27/24187164/xbox-cloud-gaming-tv-app-fire-tv-stick-amazon-launch"&gt;announced last month&lt;/a&gt;, provides access to Xbox Cloud Gaming, allowing subscribers of Xbox Game Pass Ultimate to stream a variety of Xbox titles to some Fire TV devices.&lt;/p&gt;
